(firstQuint)ORTHOVISC Shoulder Osteoarthritis Study.

 This multicenter, prospective double-blinded, randomized trial will study two treatment groups.

 Subjects will be randomized to receive either Orthovisc or corticosteroids/anesthetic injection into the shoulder in a 2:1 schema.

 The trial will assess safety and efficacy of pain relief in the osteoarthritic shoulder.

